{"tid":402254,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬不滿PSG對主射12碼的次序","createTime":"2017-09-16T09:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T12:01:53.000Z","uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7d0ebc4832afb240497c81b880182be13ca42a","tid":402254,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"巴西前鋒尼馬都可以話係今夏球壇大贏家，以破世界紀錄2.2億歐元（約19億港元）加盟巴黎聖日耳門（PSG），除稅後年薪就接近3千萬歐元（約2.6億港元），而且PSG又開季贏到唔識停，聯賽5連勝，周中歐聯又大炒些路迪，尼馬仲有咩不滿搞到唔開心呢？<br />\n據法國傳媒報導，尼馬不滿球隊對主射12碼嘅次序，PSG宜家安排烏拉圭前鋒卡雲尼係第1號劊子手，尼馬先係第2號，所以暫時聯賽入球，卡雲尼高達7個，尼馬先得4個，如果想刷數據，爭取金球獎，尼馬想連12碼都霸埋嚟射，睇吓教練艾馬利之後點安排嘞。"},{"pid":"5751601bdaf3b6f807d11e217a42c7ff442c1925","tid":402254,"uid":34490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"終於出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c30a1eb36cf382f6036b905ca62aed52b67bb1f","tid":402254,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:48:23.000Z","msg":"💪🏻"},{"pid":"8bbaa2209018433f08257072a38d90a8a818dfc1","tid":402254,"uid":143465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:49:46.000Z","msg":"發覺尼馬成日比南美同胞逼害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2883d01b5e41ec8ac9211c2ac4c2897b3e2e47fa","tid":402254,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:52:44.000Z","msg":"卡雲尼好快會被賣走"},{"pid":"b3a367807b66036039c5a74df18a8028ced34bc6","tid":402254,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發覺尼馬成日比南美同胞逼害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁卡雲尼又真係完全唔似一個前鋒既。"},{"pid":"cc8c56fbb9477ab2ac4724421e9ae8acf9ec0c8d","tid":402254,"uid":119778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:03:20.000Z","msg":"睇佢精華片真係走火入魔咁"},{"pid":"0a3f2d2ce8dce60abc8032903b5e7980952e06d1","tid":402254,"uid":19126,"like":0,"